description:
KeyFileManagement:  Records of key file management operations within specific cells, including timestamps, location, IDs, data type, format version, and progress/management ID.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the key file management operation.
- Area_Name: Name of the area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
- Id2:  Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Ancillary identifier (appears constant in sample data).
- Id4:  Ancillary identifier (appears constant in sample data).
- vsDataType: Type of data related to key file management (e.g., vsDataKeyFileManagement).
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (e.g., EricssonSpecificAttributes).
- KeyFileManagement.reportProgress:  Progress status of the key file management operation (appears empty in sample data).
- KeyFileManagement.keyFileManagementId: Unique identifier for this specific key file management record.
